metadata.name: MilkTheCow #1
metadata.description: MilkTheCow is made up 3,500 Milkers. Each one procedurally generated, custom designed & prepped to begin milking 48 hours after Mint. Each Milker is capable of producing up to 2,000 MLK a day. MLK will be used for further advancement within our MilkVerse. MLK will also be exchangeable for ETH & Bitcoin. Its time to MilkTheCow!
